                           <p>A <material>white marble</material>
                              <objectType>altar-stele</objectType>, with moulding above and below on three sides (<height unit="metre">0.90</height> ×  <width unit="metre">0.40</width> × <depth unit="metre">0.38</depth>. The relief is of a <rs type="decoration">gladiator</rs>, a <rs type="decoration">retiarius</rs>, wearing only a loin-guard, and a strap over his left shoulder, advancing to his left; he has a bare head and hair down to his shoulders. In his left hand he holds a tall <rs type="decoration" cert="low">trident</rs>, whose head is lost; in his right hand he holds a short <rs type="decoration">sword</rs>.</p>
