         <div type="translation">
            <p>Skirtos.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>For the name see Robert, Gladiateurs, 300, 104, no.44; R. Vulpe, Apulum 5 (1965), 51-66, with BullÉp 1968.361; D. French, 'Two gladiatorial texts', no.1. The sense of 'nimble' is particularly appropriate to a retiarius.</p>
         </div>
